The paper discusses the use of liveness detection in biometric authentication systems, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of software-based algorithms and system-based fingerprint liveness detection, which could fall under machine learning (cs.MM) and data mining (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the LivDet competitions, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves the evaluation of different algorithms and systems.
